So I'm sitting watching one tree hill re-runs and i get a text, from my mom. who is in the bathroom not 10 feet away. 
"how long do you think you will need to get to the babysitting thing on thursday?"  
"idk its in santa ana" 
"I'm thinking 30 to 45 min okay with u?" 
so i'm done cause HOLY SHIT so i walk to the door and yell can you wait and just talk to me? 
so she comes out and just glares at me 
"so" 
" i just don't understand why you couldn't wait to get out of the bathroom. why did you have to text me hwen i'm right here?" 
"you know i let you use my car and i pay for the gas" 
"why did you just say that?" 
"what?" 
*tired sigh* 
"Don't *sigh* at me!" 
"why did you bring up the car?" 
"because i do all that and you aren't very gracious" 
"but i don't know why that makes a difference right now ... do you not want me to do the babysitting?" 
"no i want you to *tired sigh* i just think you take advantage of me letting you use the car" 
"uhh ...* tired sigh* okay I'm sorry" 
"thats all i wanted even if you didn't mean a word" 


WTF JUST HAPPENED?!?!?!  
word for word I SWEAR  

mind you most of the time i take the car its for class or ot go get something FOR HER  
... whatever i need a car ...
